Package com.yworks.yfiles.layout.genealogy

Provides layout algorithms that are especially suited for genealogical family trees.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FamilyTreeLayout
    This layout algorithm arranges genealogical graphs (family trees).
    FamilyTreeLayoutData
    Specifies custom data for the FamilyTreeLayout.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FamilyMembersSortingPolicy
    Enum constants that specify how family members are sorted by the FamilyTreeLayout.
    FamilyType
    Enum constants that specify the node types for the FamilyTreeLayout.
    VerticalNodeAlignment
    Alignment specifier that defines that all nodes in the same layer (generation) are aligned based on their top coordinate.

Package com.yworks.yfiles.layout.genealogy Description

Provides layout algorithms that are especially suited for genealogical family trees.

The FamilyTreeLayout will arrange the family trees.

Basic Family Tree

Family tree of the Kennedy clan

Related Documentation

See the yFiles Developer's Guide section on Domain-Specific Layout Algorithms for a description of the yFiles family tree layout algorithms.
